{"tid":1646384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新型大台：休息理論","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T03:34:23.000Z","uid":81236,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ae01e9557c85067d6ee70511789a58aa6bf89cda","tid":1646384,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"人權法案緊 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n裝修唔好睇 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n唔會再有遊行 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n星期一至五：返工返學留返星期六日 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n星期六：返黎工好攰留返聽日 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n星期日：星期一啲人要返工 - 休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141214/photo/bkn-20141214204542121-1214_00822_001_02p.jpg?20141214231223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141214204542121-1214_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20141214231223&h=d16c3df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人要抗爭有時，休息有時<br />\n<br />\n但唔係長休，對方絕對唔會比機會你喘息<br />\n<br />\n勇武覺得攰既可以加入下文宣組一齊貼下牆<br />\n文宣攰既可以組埋朋友一就去懲罰下黃店<br />\n<br />\n每日都休息緊既人<br />\n<br />\n香港人同埋下一代都好需要你，你準備好一齊加入未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tKykc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tKykc0.jpg&h=90330776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qf68SOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqf68SOz.jpg&h=8beda610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3ab1ae3e7852118b937441195bf0bfd58645a89","tid":1646384,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"而家我地要做嘅，係感召其他受害人企出黎證明S 小姐係可信，而唔係浪費時間討論S 小姐是否可信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0e5d391b94e51c1bc914a50135df6e359eef62c","tid":1646384,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{